<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/616643-ms-kondo-whenever-you-talk-about-a">Ms. Kondo, Whenever you talk about a client and the number of bags that he or she discarded, there is no mention of giving clothing, shoes, or other items to a non-profit organization for others to use. I am wondering if you encourage clients to do this? It is quite acceptable in the United States. Thank you.</a>
