        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3059230567" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17272846572111649829">I just love Marie Kondo&apos;s aesthetics, her ideas and her ability to motivate me to tidy up. On any given day, I&apos;d rather read than tidy up and this book is the perfect compromise as it puts me in the mood to get rid of anything that doesn&apos;t spark joy. I can just feel myself inching my way into a minimalist life style.</span>
  <span id="freeText17272846572111649829" style="display:none">I just love Marie Kondo's aesthetics, her ideas and her ability to motivate me to tidy up. On any given day, I'd rather read than tidy up and this book is the perfect compromise as it puts me in the mood to get rid of anything that doesn't spark joy. I can just feel myself inching my way into a minimalist life style.</span>
